        <mxCell id="legend_text" value="① Detect: emotion + language + intent (planner) + route decision (FAST_CHAT / TOOL_FLOW / BLOCKED)&#xa;② Fetch context: RAG chunks (pgvector) + user memory (postgres) + birth chart (core service) + catalog items (core service) — all in parallel&#xa;③ Gates: recommendation gate (score ≥ 31) + remedy dual-choice (kya karu → simple vs detailed) + catalog guardrail (no gemstones/yantras)&#xa;④ Generate: persona prompt + style instruction + guardrails → Gemini 3.5 Flash → post-process → SSE stream to client&#xa;⑤ Async: extract 13 memory facts + track behavior + persist turns + update session state — does NOT delay response" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#555;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
